title: John Sandford - Shadow Prey (Abridged 3-CD Audiobook)
description:
*******************************************************************************
              John Sandford - Shadow Prey (Abridged 3-CD Audiobook)
*******************************************************************************

A slumlord in Minneapolis, a politician in New York City, and a judge in
Oklahoma City are all murdered in the same way. All are connected back to
Minnesota&#039;s Native American community, where Lucas Davenport must find the
elusive Shadow Love to avoid Lucas becoming the next victim.
